Package: xlsform2wordR
Type: Package
Title: Convert XLSForm to Word with Theme-Grid, Language-Aware Choices and Conditions
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Manantsoa", family = "Vagnondily", role = c("aut","cre"),
           email = "you@example.org")
)
Description: Read an XLSForm and produce a formatted Word (.docx) questionnaire. 
    Supports 'theme-grid' (settings$style), highlights relevant conditions in red,
    and substitutes choice names by localized labels based on survey label language.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    readxl,
    officer,
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    rlang
Suggests:
    flextable,
    roxygen2,
    remotes
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/vagnondily/Xlsform2wordR
BugReports: https://github.com/vagnondily/Xlsform2wordR/issues
